<p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">We are an emerging data analytics training and consultancy hub based in Zambia, committed to equipping individuals and organizations with the skills and tools needed to excel in today's data-driven world. By empowering institutions, professionals and students we aim to be at the forefront of shaping the future of analytics in Zambia and beyond.</p>
<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm mb-8">
